1
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:08,760
Selamat ulang tahun.

2
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:16,360
Apa yang kamu harapkan?

3
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,080
SAYA...

4
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:23,880
Sepertinya semangkuk mi ini
akan terbuang sia-sia.

5
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:29,080
Ayo pergi.

6
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:31,880
Hei, mereka sudah datang!

7
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:32,600
Kejar mereka!

8
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,880
Jangan biarkan mereka lolos!

9
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,040
Berhenti di situ!

10
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,680
Masuk ke dalam mobil!

11
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:33,920
Berhenti di situ!

12
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:35,800
Berhenti!

13
00:04:21,520 --> 00:04:22,200
Halo.

14
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,560
Dua kamar,

15
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,920
Lima ribu yuan.

16
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,520
Hanya satu kamar.

17
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,360
Paspor Anda.

18
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,440
Wanita,

19
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,560
Ini pacarku.

20
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,800
Kami baru saja mulai berpacaran.

21
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,520
Bisakah kamu membantuku?

22
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,120
Kamar 202.

23
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,200
Kamu mandi dulu.

24
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,320
Aku akan menunggu di luar.

25
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,480
Sudah selesai?

26
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:48,800
Ya.

27
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,800
Teruskan.

28
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,280
Kamu terluka.

29
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,400
Apakah kamu melakukan ini pada semua gadis?

30
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,720
Apakah seperti itu caramu melihatku?

31
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,680
Malam itu, kau dan Zhu Wenjie...

32
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:17,800
Apakah kamu cemburu?

33
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,440
Kamu tidak tidur?

34
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,920
Apa hubungannya dengan saya?

35
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,560
Aku hanya melakukan ini padamu.

36
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,040
Rasanya tetap enak.

37
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:17,200
Terima kasih.
Silakan ambil lagi.
